{"tid":1720671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求中大化學教授出來查中大同全港二噁英","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:56:36.000Z","uid":232237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"505ef80891027d0cdd4afa60662779a5c8acd059","tid":1720671,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f282acc3efaa96c1ba200a6047b5c280d561eb","tid":1720671,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"505ef80891027d0cdd4afa60662779a5c8acd059","tid":1720671,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ae3a3414628d894dbdedadb610f2ed3d5c763a","tid":1720671,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"116ee40543e704e3e7da8059f1b75d709da10991","tid":1720671,"uid":24621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c9984e5be72d048c00cacf846134cf4ff153675","tid":1720671,"uid":266780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:21:56.000Z","msg":"中大化學/生化 相關的人, 入一入嚟<br />\n<br />\n可否請各位化學/生化相關學系的UG/PG/PROF, 做一下高濃度TG的殘留研究。<br />\n殘留在路上, 樹葉上, 欄桿上等. 又例如100米後, 200米後,500米後, 1K後的數量。 鞋底會否把TG或其他有毒物帶回家，數量又有多少?<br />\n<br />\n趁呢幾日未落雨, 可否快快取SAMPLE。<br />\n<br />\n因為最近身邊很多人(藍的)都有皮膚問題,<br />\n這兩天又有家人報告話很多在TG放題區的海味鋪/萬X (X寧), 在做大特價, 送禮品清貨。<br />\n我好怕大家都掂到3手TG (鞋踩過TG放題區, 再帶返屋企, 小朋友不出門都掂到)。<br />\n雖然大家都知有害，但無數據, 無REPORT (有公信力的), 咬班狗唔入的 (你見今日警謊會, 大大聲話唔關佢地事)。<br />\n亦可以提醒巿民如何自保。<br />\n<br />\n我知中大的兄弟都好攰, 但總有D人唔會行都咁前 ,例如 體弱的, 怕死的(我都怕, 家中有大有細), 有D年紀的(PROF) 。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山, 除了各有各做, 仲有個重點, 係有D山,只有你可以爬, 你唔爬,無人爬呀 (我呢D讀EEE出身的, 你叫我做都做唔到。)<br />\n<br />\n唔該兄弟"},{"pid":"a517b4ae015788d26ce5bd8263922e4f1b55f2a6","tid":1720671,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:21:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4efc034dc442c71052a27c1a5eb601b86d20644","tid":1720671,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"提醒返，之後已經有巴打度左街上面山埃濃度係爆哂"},{"pid":"3812f814729b6fd10e323589b33fc67d335bbf50","tid":1720671,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f692f35b4a9e46c125f47a4e15bf33f64fcde10","tid":1720671,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s